  <brief_title>Preoperative Mindfulness: Minimally Invasive Hysterectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Mindfulness In Patients Undergoing Minimally Invasive Hysterectomy: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
